verses.1: Ka mite aw, keima hilhna ngai unla, ka kam tawh ka thugente na bil uh hong ngat un.
verses.2: Note tungah thu gentehna zangin ka kam ka-in thu kong gen ding hi. I pu i pate in hong gen sa, eite in i zak sa le i theih sa, tanglai-a thuthukte ka hong gen khia ding hi.
verses.4: Hih thute, i tate tungah eite in im loin, a hong piang lai ding khang thakte tungah, Topaʼ minthang nasepna, ama vangliatna, ama sep sa nalamdangte i gen ding hi.
verses.5: Amaute pen Pasian tungah a lungsim thuman lo, lungsim kip a nei lo khangmi, lungsim khauhin a lehdo khangmi, amauʼ pu le pate tawh kibang loin, amaute in Pasian sungah amauʼ lametna koihin, Pasianʼ nasepnate mangngilh loin, ama thupiakte zui-in, a suak nai lo naupangte, a hong piangkik khang thakte in a thu thei-in, amaute ding khia-in amauʼ tuletate tungah a thu a gen theih nadingin, amah in, i pate in a tate a hilh sawn dinga a sawl ahi, Israel sungah thukham khat koihin, Jakob sungah teci panna khat a koih hi.
verses.9: Thal a tawi Efraim mite, gal kido ni-in nungkik uh hi.
verses.10: Amaute in Pasianʼ thuciamna zui lo uh a, ama thukham bangin gamta nuam lo uh hi.
verses.11: Ama bawl sa le amaute tungah nalamdang a lah sate amaute in mangngilh uh hi.
verses.12: Egypt gam sung Zoan munah, a pu a pate uhʼ muhna ah amah in nalamdang a bawl hi.
verses.13: Amah in tuipi kikhensakin amaute kantansak a, tuite a lompi-in a omsak hi.
verses.14: Sun hunin amah in amaute meiipi khat tawh kha a, zan tawntung, meikuang taang khat tawh amaute a kha hi.
verses.15: Amah in gam sungah suangpite kitamsak a, tui thukpi sung panin a piang khia bangin amauteʼ tungah tui dawn ding tampi a pia hi.
verses.16: Amah in suangpi sung panin luitui luang khiasak a, gun tui luang bangin tuite a luangsak hi.
verses.17: Ahi zongin ama tungah amaute khial lailai uh a, Sehnel gam sungah Sangpen pa a lehpan uh hi.
verses.18: Amaute in amauʼ duh mahmah an a kalhna uh tawh amaute in a lungsim sung uh ah Pasian a ze-et uh hi.
verses.19: Amaute in Pasian gensia uh a, “Pasian in gamlak ah an pia thei ding ahi hiam?
verses.20: Amah in suangpi sat a, tui leng khia-in tuite dim let takpi ahi hiam? Amah in ama mite, an ahi a, sameh ahi zongin a pia thei takpi ahi hiam?” a ci uh hi.
verses.21: Topa in tua thu a zak ciangin hehna tawh kidimin, meikuang tawh Jakob su gawp a, Israel tungah a heh semsem hi.
verses.22: Bang hang hiam cih leh amaute in Pasian um lo uh a, a hon khia zo dingin muang lo uh hi.
verses.23: Ahi zongin amah in, tunga om vantungte thu pia-in, vantung kongte hong a,
verses.24: nek dingin amau tungah manna an zusakin, amaute tungah vantung an a pia hi.
verses.25: Mihingte in vantung miteʼ an ne uh a, amah in amaute tungah an tampi a puak hi.
verses.26: Amah in vantungah nisuahna huih nungsakin, ama vangliatna tawh leitaw lam huih paikhiatpih a,
verses.27: amah in amaute tungah leivui zah-a tam sa zusak a, tuipi sehnel zah-a tam vasate a khiat suk hi.
verses.28: Amauʼ giahphual laizang, amauʼ omna kiim khempeuh ah tuate a kiasak hi.
verses.29: Amauʼ duh pen pia ahih manin, amaute in ne-in gilvah uh hi.
verses.30: Ahih hangin amaute in a duh pen uh a kham ma, amauʼ kam sungah an a om laipi mahin,
verses.31: amauteʼ tungah Pasianʼ hehna tungkikin amah in amaute lakah a hat pen teng thatin, Israel-teʼ muan le suan teng a vatlum hi.
verses.32: Hih nalamdangte khempeuh a om khin hi napi-in amaute khial lai veve uh a, ama nalamdangteʼ hangin amaute in um tuan lo uh hi.
verses.33: Tua ahih ciangin amah in amauʼ hunte husan khat bangin maimangsak a, amauʼ nuntakna, launa lianpi tawh a beisak hi.
verses.34: Amaute pawl khat a thah khit ciangin a om lai mite in amah zong pan uh hi. Amaute kisikin, lungsim taktak tawh Pasian a zong uh hi.
verses.35: Amaute in Pasian pen, amaute a hon khia, Sangpen Pasian, amaute a hupa ahihna a phawk uh hi.
verses.36: Ahih hangin amaute in a kampi bek uh tawh amah phat khem uh a, a leii uh tawh ama tungah zuaugen uh hi.
verses.37: Amauteʼ lungsim ama lamah kip lo uh a, ama thuciamna ah amaute thuman lo uh hi.
verses.38: Ahi zongin amah in hehpihna lungsim nei ahih manin amauʼ khialhnate maisakin, amaute susia lo hi. Amah in a hehna ip zelzel a, a hehna khempeuh phong khia lo hi.
verses.39: Amah in, amaute pen mihing hi lel a, a hong paikik nawn lo huihnung bang ahihna uh a phawk hi.
verses.40: Amaute in gamlak ah amah lehdo zelzel uh a, sehnel gam sungah amah dahsak uh hi.
verses.41: Amaute in amah ze-et kikkik uh a, Israel-teʼ Siangtho Pasian a phin uh hi.
verses.42: Galteʼ kiang panin amah in amaute a hotkhiat ni hitaleh, Egypt gamah ama limte a bawl hun lai hitaleh, Zoan gamah a bawl a nalamdangte hitaleh, ama vangliatna hitaleh, amaute in ngaihsutin nei lo uh hi.
verses.44: Amaute in a lui tuite uh a dawn theih loh nadingin amauʼ gun tuite amah in sisan a suaksak hi.
verses.45: Amaute a pet thei cippi honte, amauteʼ lote a susia uiphukte amauʼ lakah a sawl hi.
verses.46: Amauʼ lo ante tangngol pia a, amauʼ sepna gahte kauphe a pia hi.
verses.47: A leengguite uh gial tawh deng gawp a, a theithekte uh vukkhal tawh susia hi.
verses.48: A ganhingte uh gial tawh deng lum a, a gan khawite uh keek tawh a deng lum hi.
verses.49: Amauteʼ tungah a lauhuai ama sinsona, hehna, thangpaihna, gimna, le a susia thei van mi hon khat a khah hi.
verses.50: Amah in a sinsona ip loin, kuamah hinkhawi lo a, pulnatna tawh amaute a sisak hi.
verses.51: Hamʼ suanteʼ inn sungah a ta upa pen teng, Egypt gam sung tacil khempeuh amah in a vatmai hi.
verses.52: Tua ciangin amah in tua bangin ama mite gamlak ah paikhiat pihin, ganhing honpi bangin amaute a paipih hi.
verses.53: Amah in a muanhuaina munah amaute paipih ahih manin amaute lau lo uh hi. Ahih hangin tuipi in amauʼ galte tuumcip hi.
verses.54: A khut taklam tawh ama ngah sa mual ahi, a gam siangtho ah amaute a paipih hi.
verses.55: Amauʼ mai panin midangte hawl khia-in, amauteʼ luah ding neihsa hawmsak a, Israel minamte amauʼ buk sungah a tengsak hi.
verses.56: Ahi zongin amaute in Sangpen Pasian ze-etin lehdo uh a, ama thupiakna zui loin,
verses.57: a pu a pate uh mah bangin kihei khia-in a zuau gamtat uh hi. Thal gina lo bangin amaute a kihuiheek uh hi.
verses.58: Bang hang hiam cih leh amaute in a mun sangte uh tawh amah a sin so nadingin phinphin uh a, amauʼ milim bawlte tawh ama hazat nading a piangsak uh hi.
verses.59: Pasian in a zak ciangin heh pha mahmah a, amah in Israel-te a nial siangtho hi.
verses.60: Mihingteʼ lakah ama omna puanbuk ahi, Shiloh khua-a ama omna biakinn nusia a,
verses.61: ama vangliatna, galteʼ tungah ap a, ama minthanna, galteʼ khut ah a pia hi.
verses.62: Amah in ama mite namsau tawh sisak a, ama luahte tungah a hehna a nga hi.
verses.63: Mei in a tangvalte kaang lum a, a nungakteʼ pasal ding kuamah om nawn lo hi.
verses.64: Amauʼ siampite, namsau in puksak a, amauʼ zite in a pasalte kah zo lo uh hi.
verses.65: Tua ciangin Topa pen zukhamin a awng mi thahatpa, a ihmu tho bangin a khanglo hi.
verses.66: Amah in a langpangte zo a, a maizum tawntung dingin amaute a koih hi.
verses.67: Amah in Josefʼ suante nial a, Efraim minamte teel lo hi.
verses.68: Ahih hangin ama it Zion Mual, Judah minam a teel hi.
verses.69: A kip den dingin a phuh sa leitang bang leh, a vantung inn bangin ama biakinn a lam hi.
verses.70: Amah in ama mi Jakob, ama luah Israel a cing dingin, no a nei tuupite a cinna, tuubukte panin la-in, ama nasem David a teel hi.
verses.72: Amah in lungsim thutang tawh amaute hoihtakin cingin, a siam mahmah a khut tawh amaute lam a lak hi.
